{"FAKE":[{"def":"One of the circles or windings of a cable or hawser, as it lies in a coil; a single turn or coil.","pos":""}],"FAKER":[{"def":"One who fakes something, as a thief, a peddler of petty things, a workman who dresses things up, etc.","pos":""}],"FAKIR":[{"def":"An Oriental religious ascetic or begging monk.","pos":""}]}